start
run shake function to generate boggle board with randomize alphabet
get the words string from dictionary file & convert to array
for each word in words array
  check the word status
  is the first char of the word exist on the game board?
  if available, do boggle check
    check in 3x3 around the coordinate of the word, is the next char for the word available?
    if available, do boggle check again (in recursive), until the last char of the word
  is all the char on the word exist and fulfill all the boggle check?
  if true, mark the word as a result
count all boggle words
result print all boggle word(s) found
end
